    
::AddOverlay [widget nobr]
/* adds an overlay to the following "continue button".

ex:
<<AddOverlay "int">>

if there's no overlay, you must call it without any arguments!

<<AddOverlay>>

$args[0] = overlay*/
<<widget "AddOverlay">>
    <<if $args[0]>>
        <<set _overlay to $args[0]>>
    <<else>>
        <<set _overlay to false>>
    <</if>>
    <<set $overlays.push(_overlay)>>
<</widget>>